<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0961825103/hip-20" TARGET="Window209">Systemantics :
The Underground Text of Systems Lore: How Systems Really Work and How They Fail</A>  	Gall, John		1975

General Systemantics Press, 3200 W. Liberty Rd., Ann Arbor, MI 48103

</TT></PRE>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=8>
