<PRE><TT>
<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0819171123/hip-20"  TARGET="Window301">Conflict and Defense: A General Theory</A>			Boulding, Kenneth    1962
Harper Torchbooks

</TT></PRE>
