<PRE><TT>

<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1584230703/hip-20" TARGET="Window879"><IMG SRC="HIP/1584230703.01.TZZZZZZZ.jpg" border="0" alt="cover" hspace="3" vspace="3"></A>
<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1584230703/hip-20" TARGET="Window879">The Medium is the Massage -- An Inventory of Effects</A>	McLuhan, Marshall &	1967
Bantam Books, New York					Fiore, Quinton	
								co-ordinated by Jerome Agel

</TT></PRE>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=8>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<B><FONT SIZE=+2>IDEAS:</FONT></B> <!-- ToDo -->
</TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial" SIZE=+1>
art, fragmentation, global village
</FONT>
<P>
</TD>
