<PRE><TT>

<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0451136950/hip-20" TARGET="Window799">Limits to Growth: A Report for the Club of Rome</A>				Meadows, et. al.	1972
The New American Library
1301 Ave. of the Americas, New York, NY 10019

