<PRE><TT>

<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0691024170/hip-20" TARGET="753"><IMG SRC="HIP/0691024170.01.TZZZZZZZ.jpg" border="0" alt="cover" hspace="3" vspace="3"></A>
<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0691024170/hip-20" TARGET="753">QED</A>								Feynman, Richard	1985
Princeton University Press, Princeton, NJ

