<PRE><TT>

<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1855840553/hip-20" TARGET="Window555"><IMG SRC="HIP/1855840553.01.TZZZZZZZ.jpg" border="0" alt="cover" hspace="3" vspace="3"></A>
<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1855840553/hip-20" TARGET="Window555">Sensitive Chaos: The Creation of Flowing Forms in Water and Air</A>		Schwenk, Theodor	1965
Schocken Books, 200 Madison Ave., New York, NY 10016 [out of print!!!]

</TT></PRE>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=8>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
