we'll have no need for slaves."

                -- Aristotle </FONT><TT>

<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0893470023/hip-20" TARGET="Window442">Computer Lib/Dream Machines</A>					Nelson, Ted  1974
Aperture

</TT></PRE>
<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=8>
<TR>
