<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/013937681X/hip-20" TARGET="Window205"><IMG SRC="HIP/013937681X.01.TZZZZZZZ.jpg" border="0" alt="cover" hspace="3" vspace="3"></A>
<A HREF="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/013937681X/hip-20" TARGET="Window205">The UNIX  Programming Environment</A> 				Kernighan, Brain W., &
Prentice-Hall, Inc., Englewood Cliffs, NJ 07632		Pike, Rob		1984

</TT></PRE>
<TABLE BORDER=0>
<TR>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<B><FONT SIZE=+2>IDEAS:</FONT></B> <!-- ToDo -->
</TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial" SIZE=+1>
