isco....> <A HREF="/research/Design_prototype_chip_makes_possible_a_fully_implantable__cochlear_implant.asp">Full Article</A></P><HR><H2><A Class="H2" HREF="/research/Cochlear_implants_--_with_no_exterior_hardware.asp">Cochlear implants -- with no exterior hardware (2/12/2014)</A></H2><P>Researchers develop cochlear implant that can be wirelessly recharged....> <A HREF="/research/Cochlear_implants_--_with_no_exterior_hardware.asp">Full Article</A></P><HR><H2><A Class="H2" HREF="/research/New_high-tech_prosthetics_and_orthotics_offer_active_life-style_for_users.asp">New, high-tech prosthetics and orthotics offer active life-style for users (2/9/2014)</A></H2><P>Comparative research into the effectiveness of advanced prosthetic and orthotics technologies is the focus of the current special issue of Technology and Innovation-Proceedings of the National Academy of Inventors....> <A HREF="/research/New_high-tech_prosthetics_and_orthotics_offer_active_life-style_for_users.asp">Full Article</A></P><HR><H2><A Class="H2" HREF="/research/A_microchip_for_metastasis.asp">A microchip for metastasis (2/8/2014)</A></H2><P>A new microfluidic platform shows how cancer cells invade specific organs....> <A HREF="/research/A_microchip_for_metastasis.asp">Full Article</A></P>
