              "http://flashpoint1.silverstream.tv/flashplayer.aspx?id=139">his talk</a>
              to the Institute of Direct Marketing <a href=
              "http://www.theidm.com/events/annual-idm-lunch/">2009 Annual Lunch</a> in
              London. He is best known for his book with Anthony Willams <a href=
