              <h4>Oliver Selfridge</h4>

              <p>Alex Andrew writes: The death of Oliver Selfridge on 3rd December is
              <a href=
              "http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/us/04selfridge.html">reported</a> in the
              New York Times. (Registration is required for free access.)</p>

              <p>He was the grandson of the man who founded the London store, and active
              in the Lincoln Laboratory of MIT and author of the important "<a href=
              "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oliver_Selfridge">Pandemonium</a>" paper in
              the 1958 Teddington Symposium. He was 82.</p>
