              <h4 align="center"><a class="plain" href=
              "http://www.cs.ucla.edu/~cyber/">Cybernetics at UCLA</a></h4>

              <p>The Bruin <a href=
              "http://www.dailybruin.ucla.edu/news/articles.asp?id=31028">reports</a>.
              "The time of cybernetics has come", said program chair <a href=
              "http://www.cs.ucla.edu/csd/people/faculty_pages/distefano.html">Joe
              DiStefano</a>. "These tools have been around for a long time, but their
              utility and power wasn't recognized because the demand wasn't great
              enough."</p>

              <p><a href="http://www.cs.ucla.edu/~cyber/methodology_desc.htm">Core
              material</a> includes Cybernetics, Biomodelling, Probability, Statistics,
              Systems and Signals, Feedback Control Systems, Modelling and
              Simulation.</p>
              <hr />

