              <h4>Cybernetics News</h4>

              <h5>Can Baxter bring more manufacturing back to the west?</h5>

              <p>Robotics guru Rodney Brooks who gave us the vacuum cleaning <a href=
              "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roomba">Roomba</a> robot has launched
              <a href="http://www.rethinkrobotics.com/">Rethink Robotics</a> first
              product Baxter, a low cost conveyer belt worker.</p>

              <p>IEEE Spectrum <a href=
              "http://spectrum.ieee.org/robotics/industrial-robots/rethink-robotics-baxter-robot-factory-worker">
              reports</a>.</p>
