              <h5>Ear-like system could clear up cellphone conversations</h5>

              <p>Professor Parham Aarabi of U of Toronto Department of Electrical and
              Computer Engineering says "This system employs two microphones that, just
              like the two human ears, focus on the speaker's voice and filter out other
              noises." <a href=
