              <h5>Human-Built World: How to Think About Technology and Culture</h5>

              <p>Review by Mark Archer in FT of Thomas Hughes' book.</p>

              <p>"...it is almost chilling to learn that the term "feedback" - so prized
              in the workplace and focus groups - was coined by Weiner to describe "the
              use of controlling signals to modify the output, or behaviour, of a machine
              or organism so that it will reach its goal".<a href=
