<!-- ### End Engineering Home Header, copied from MTD Home Header #### --><a name="d.en.130739"></a>
<div style="border: 1px #ccc solid; margin: 10px 0 10px 0; padding: 10px;">
<h1 style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Welcome to Engineering and Informatics</h1>
<p style="line-height: 1.5em;">Engineering and Informatics delivers an exciting mix of core engineering disciplines and creative technologies that complement each other in terms of delivering innovative solutions with high sector impact to the challenges posed by industry, the environment, and health and well-being agendas, and providing our students with a wide range of expertise and opportunity that individuals can tailor to their particular strengths.</p>
</div>	<ul class="square-nav-buttons-220">
		
		<span class="introBox"><div style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<h2 style="font-size: 140%; font-weight: normal; margin: 10px 10px 5px 10px; padding: 0;">Academic Structure</h2>
<p style="font-size: 90%; font-weight: normal; margin: 10px; padding: 0; line-height: 1.4em;">To support activity, delivery, and innovation across disciplines whilst recognising natural complementary disciplines, Engineering and Informatics is organised into three Schools: School of Electrical Engineering &amp; Computer Science, School of Engineering, School of Media, Design and Technology.</p>
</div></span>
		
		
			
		<li>
			<a href='/ei/electrical-engineering-and-computer-science/'>
				<div class="bg" style='background: url(/ei/eecs.jpg)'>
