<h1>Undergraduate Study at Bradford</h1>
<p><strong>At the University of Bradford, a degree is more than a qualification</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Student life at Bradford is an adventure to be shared with new friends,&nbsp;<a href="/undergraduate/student-life/">on campus</a>, <a href="/the-city-of-bradford/">in the city</a>, or even <a href="/undergraduate/your-career/study-abroad/">studying abroad</a>.</li>
<li>Studying at Bradford is the gateway to <a href="/undergraduate/your-career/">your future career</a>; an investment for the rest of your life.</li>
<li>As one of <a href="/undergraduate/meet-our-students-and-graduates/">our students</a>, you won&rsquo;t just graduate &ndash; you&rsquo;ll grow, develop and flourish and learn how to be a <a href="/undergraduate/student-life/">global citizen</a>.</li>
<li>Our courses are sculpted with <a href="/undergraduate/your-career/international-industry-partnerships/">industry input</a> from many of the employers who will be sifting through your CV.</li>
<li>You&rsquo;ll be taught by the <a href="/undergraduate/meet-your-lecturers/">academic experts</a> whose <a href="/undergraduate/meet-your-lecturers/our-research-impact/">pioneering research</a> is shaping the very future of those industries.</li>
<li>Put your theory into practise in our&nbsp;<a href="/undergraduate/campus-and-facilities/">world-class facilities</a> and then on a <a href="/undergraduate/your-career/work-placements/">work placement</a> with some of the world&rsquo;s biggest names.</li>
</ul>	<ul class="square-nav-buttons-220x3">
		
			
		<li>
